Cloth Sharing Website
This is a Django web app for a cloth sharing website.
Users can create accounts, list their clothes, and borrow clothes from other users.

Installation
Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/BS-PMC-2023/BS-PMC-2023-Team18
Create a virtual environment: python3 -m venv venv
Activate the virtual environment: source venv/bin/activate
Install dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt
Create a local database: python manage.py migrate
Create a superuser: python manage.py createsuperuser
Run the server: python manage.py runserver
Usage
Navigate to http://localhost:8000/ in your web browser.
Sign up for an account or log in with an existing account.
List clothes that you are willing to share or browse clothes that other users have listed.
Request to borrow a piece of clothing or accept a request to lend your clothing.
Return the borrowed clothing within the agreed upon time frame.
Contributing
Contributions are welcome! Please submit a pull request with your changes.
